Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.42,0:00:04.69,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As long as modern-day crimes involve people,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:06.52,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}there are no unsolvable mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:08.66,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's case is about Conan's origin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:10.46,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the detective from out west\Nmakes a reappearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:12.43,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:14.67,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:16.97,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:47.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Sherlock Holmes Enthusiasts Reception Tour"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A Study in Scarlet"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:48.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is noteworthy as the very first story Sherlock Holmes appears in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The Red-Headed League" is my favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mine's "The Sign of Four"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! That one was internationally acclaimed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impressive, my boy! You can read kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to go on this stupid tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} applied for you without asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then I was unlucky enough to get picked...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which story do you favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd say I prefer "And Then There Was One."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's "And Then There Were None."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:37.94,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Toshiaki Fujisawa (47)\NTrain Station Attendant
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that novel was written by Agatha Christie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:45.41,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nanako Shimizu (24)\NLibrarian
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,not my beloved Conan Doyle{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My word.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:49.87,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ikuo Kawatsu (25)\NHigh School Gym Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who let this amateur on the tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about a real party pooper...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to live with these jerks for three whole days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These aren't the only guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:04.05,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hitomi Iwai (24)\NLodge Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the tour director is in another car,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,taking the other guests back to the lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. The more the merrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give you merrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome, everyone, to the Mycroft Lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Kanaya, the director of this tour
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:23.37,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki Kanaya (51)\NLodge Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and this lodge's owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each one of you here today
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is a superior Sherlockian that I have carefully selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:32.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you were careful enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems a complete amateur who knows nothing about Holmes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is there really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:41.26,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Maria Toda (43)\NFortuneteller
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there. That mustached man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:42.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it. I'm out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This man I've brought here today is none other
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,than the great, modern-day detective that compares with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,our beloved Holmesâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:04:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen him many a time on TV and in the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He certainly appears to have a superior intellect,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:12.62,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kento Togano (22)\NUniversity Student\NLogic Studies Club President
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he clearly doesn't compare with Sherlock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:18.09,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ayako Oki (21)\NUniversity Student\NLogic Studies Club Member
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a real contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you probably wouldn't even begin to compare to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't let them get away with saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're being compared with Holmes; it's to be expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:24.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I refuse to lose to a stupid fictional character!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, this is all because you signed me up for this tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Your name's Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Truly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I like it too! Isn't it a great name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I didn't need to worry after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s usually cool and strangely un-childlike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But as I look at that innocent face of his, I feel relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:05:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s fascination with Holmes is almost the same as his!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know who!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's snobbish and arrogant,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a mystery nerd, a Holmes freak, and is tone-deaf,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but a superb high school soccer player,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the guy who ran off during our contest the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before I could recoup my losses...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Shin'ichi Kudo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a Holmes fan too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason I applied for this tour
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was 'cuz I thought I might find Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, Ellery Queen's much better than Conan Doyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On second thought, maybe Doyle's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's growing late, so we'll call it a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Breakfast is tomorrow morning at 9:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,lunch at 1:00, and dinner at 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then after dinner is the annual super-difficult mystery quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And those who get a perfect score on the quiz
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,will be presented with Conan Doyle's greatest work
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which brought Sherlock Holmes into this worldâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a first-edition copy of "A Study in Scarlet!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, I must see proof of how devoted you are to Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What my maid is passing out right now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is the Holmes Cult Test of 1000 Questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1000 questions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have until dinner tomorrow evening to turn it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only those who get over 990 correct
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,will be able to participate in tomorrow's quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to be safe, if you have a cell phone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or any Holmes-related literature,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,please hand them over to my maid now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no point in trying to hide them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Placed throughout the lodge to watch over you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are security cameras and listening devices!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're caught cheating, you will be asked to leave at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now. Do I have to take that test too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Certainly not; you're a special guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I ask is that you give us a lecture later on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. If I get over 990 right, can I be in the quiz too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:12.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"What was the exact date that Holmes fell
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:18.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}to the bottom of the valley with Professor Moriarty?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}May 4th, 1891.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:23.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is actually pretty easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:24.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Next one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:27.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Write down the entire code from 'The Dancing Men'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}exactly as it appeared."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you still up? It's 4 o'clock, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh. No TV, no phones, no newspapers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, there's not even any air-conditioning,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,despite this heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A single security camera is all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:47.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owner hasn't shown up at all, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go get him and start grading the tests already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I've been told to entertain you all until he comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:16.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kudo ain't here. I shouldn't have come on this tour...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it! I've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like the rumors were true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was lying when he said he would give away
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that first-edition copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He finds fault in people's answers every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and makes it so nobody ever wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He only holds this tour to show off that book of his!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm going to sleep too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous. I'm going to bed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, man. I'm at my limit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:09:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kento. Let's go back to our room, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be patient! Making a move at a time like this would mean defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't that the car we came in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the owner! He's driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the mystery quiz is finally starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my Kento.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a cliff there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's speeding up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mister! What're you doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop the car before you drive off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's a blanket on the car's panel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:37.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And what's that sound?! It's not the engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mister! I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? The owner's dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He drove off the cliff just now before our very eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be! Why would he do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably didn't want to part with his first-edition book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this just might've been a murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone put him to sleep or killed him in advance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,sat him in the car seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:29.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and put the car in drive to make it move forward automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer most likely did all of that inside that garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then does that mean one of us is the killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That may be, but the car sped up at one point!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:45.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was also a strange hissing sound coming from inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't the engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that must have been the air conditioner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The AC was set to on, so when the engine was started
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it kicked in by itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, the body is unrecoverable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:11:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our only choice is to contact the police and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the owner took all our phones...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must be in his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? What are you looking at that tire track for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just looking for something...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not you too, Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me! I was just checking to see
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if the AC was really on or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then I run into this kid againâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:26.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:31.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He also collided with me when I was looking for evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:33.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}during that previous incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too dark to see well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's this, young detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:43.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Much obliged...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The phones have been demolished!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first-edition book is gone too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it! I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's take the remaining car and get out of this placeâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car in the garage had its gas tank punctured
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and all the gasoline has leaked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, the battery's been removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car's not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would seem the owner was killed by someone, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of trick the killer used to speed the car up is a mystery,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the fact that we're trapped here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,means that the killer still plans to continue this murder drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case, the killer is in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we properly investigate we'll uncover them soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! The security cameras might have recorded something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Those aren't real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He puts them up every year for this tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With thumbtacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thumbtacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, we know it was around 3:30
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when the killer put the owner in the car and sent him on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that it was impossible for the five of us
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who had been in the living room for several hours prior
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the killer was one of us five who weren't in the living room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please refrain from counting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find what you were looking for earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayako?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just figured out both the killer's identity and their trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with conclusive evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give you 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't wish to hear your name from my mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then you'll come clean before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayako! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy? The killer might go after you if you're all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, but you'll protect me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your big reputation's on the line, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's probably bluffin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! She must have found a clue we don't know about yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, Ayako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was acting odd this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ran into her on the way back to my room after lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when she saw me, she quickly hid some papers behind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:27.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it might've been the Holmes test that was passed out last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The test?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...she was cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about low...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Who's the killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You secretly asked her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she wouldn't tell even me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:43.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then shut herself up in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it! How dare she taunt us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were other people besides Ayako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who skipped lunch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Just Kento Togano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Nanako Shimizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:04.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}At any rate, the fact that she's suspected of cheating
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}means that Ayako knew from the very start
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:10.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}that those security cameras were mock-ups!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Ayako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} come to your room this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I did the rest of the test in my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but nobody came.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:27.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means she did see it in someone's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:30.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something significant to this incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:32.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something that one of those four alibi-less people hadâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}â€”in their room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't Ayako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} late coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been over twenty minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Ayako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Ayako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's all the racket?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's rude of you to gather around the bathroom, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we were worried about you, soâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:16:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd like you to tell us who the killer is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bah. So it really was a bluff...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:14.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why? Why'd she suddenly change her attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:18.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! And there're so many things I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Ayako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She went for a walk outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We tried to stop her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she insisted there won't be any more murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we do have all four suspects here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing will happen if we just stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It came from the garage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Ayako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayako! Ayako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You moron! Jump into that and you'll only burn to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody get an extinguisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please! Somebody put it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise that book will beâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayako! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you there?! Ayako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayako?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayako! Ayako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from her clothes and figure, there's no question it's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she was perfectly fine just a short while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, she did say she figured out who the killer was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:50.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the killer killed her to keep her quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I believe all the suspects were in the owner's lodge
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when the fire erupted in this garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then who set it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't just start by itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there is one person who could have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He drove off the cliff, but wouldn't everything fit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if he were still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! If it had been a dummy or something in the car, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a novel like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope. It was the owner, in the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him too! I don't think there's any question about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then who the hell did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody's just killed Ayako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, it's painfully clear that the killer is not one of us 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, let's retreat to the house and wait until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's stay in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As if I'd ever mistake a person for a dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But all the suspects were in the lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:19:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could someone have put a time-activated detonator in the garage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there was nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how did the killer start the fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know that, so that's why we'reâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was Ayako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} doing in the garage, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really coming down...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this downpour keeps up, there's no leaving come morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm tired from staying up all night, not to mention hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall I make some coffee and something cold to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd be worried if you two girls were all by yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if the owner really is the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why would he pretend to die and then kill Ayako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's enjoying his murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a look at this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had I not been careful I would've been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If you want the book, then come to the garage at 5 AM tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll put it beneath the back seat."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was past 4:30 when the fire started in the garage...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The back seat? That's where Ayako's body was!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, where did you get this card?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was stuck in my door when I returned from dinner last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! I figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to say it?! The owner was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I really trust what a kid saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:34.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Judging from where Ayako{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} died,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:37.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}it would seem that she, too, went to the garage to get the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:41.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means the only remaining mystery of the second incident
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:45.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}is how the killer lit the garage on fire while still in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's because of detectives like you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that so many cases go unsolved...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My dad solves his cases every single time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He takes a sleeping-like pose whenever he analyzes things,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so everyone fears him as "Sleeping Kogoro"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is he when your old man starts analyzing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, the one who's always hangin' around you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, he never is around...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, but he often appears from behind my dad
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and helps explain his theories!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:25.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From behind him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You help from behind him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I love to play detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A power outage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it from lightning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! It's just a blown fuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then hurry and reset the circuit breakers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:40.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Now, of all times!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, Miss. Use this light...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An ice pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry with the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fujisawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! The window glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit! They smashed the window and escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:11.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No! The killer's still in here! Andâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:16.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And now I finally know how the killer set the garage on fire
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:18.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}while in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the third incident wasn't part of the killer's plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.98,0:23:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.05,0:23:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm just a kid, so what would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.05,0:24:00.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This kid isn't pretending to be a detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:01.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's analyzing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.66,0:24:04.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His voice and body are different, but he's almost like Shin'ichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.93,0:24:08.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could he really be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.15,0:24:14.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.99,0:24:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's hint: Holmes' Cult Test
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.14,0:24:22.09,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, Conan's true identity is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.59,0:24:24.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Did I figure it out?
